<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>قال <span class="c2">(ع)</span>: للناس فيه ثلاثة أقوال <span class="c2">(١١٠٩)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قلت:</span> قد ذكرها <span class="c2">(ح)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
